title: LF Jungler for a 5s team
body:
We are a fun group of players that are looking for a jungler to finish off our team so we can start to climb.
Our team consists of an average rank of gold. I am the lowest at silver and highest at diamond. We need a jungler who is happy to play the engage champions but there always room for the odd assassin.

add me in game, snugglemuffin and we can do some trial games to see if you like me and the same back

Must have Skype, normal times to play will be week nights ( not Thursday or Friday ) and weekends. happy to move around for others.

replies.body:
X-diamond 4 jungler here (if that even matters :P). Im keen to get down with some team 5's. Non of my mates are into league much so i been meaning to find a group to jam some games err week.
